{"tid":1467953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"航空霸業 2.0","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:18.000Z","uid":244943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"25d42d750f5d2ac1605e166662a44a1a7703bc90","tid":1467953,"uid":244943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:42.000Z","msg":"諗著寫隻新版本，唔知咁得唔得：<br />\n<br />\n咪有幾個入口，阻淨一個入口，等部份班機可以走得。咁樣只要旅客嘅航班冇取消，佢就可以出境，唔會有班機起飛但乘客留低嘅情況。取消咗嘅航班，航空公司可以早啲通知乘客。現場嘅手足坐返兩日有咁上下經驗可以幫手傳遞訊息，如果有需要就幫旅客同職員交涉，做埋機管局嗰份。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣會唔會多啲人課金?"},{"pid":"ea37045212fbce89e50c638071968c8bccf4477f","tid":1467953,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:13.000Z","msg":"唔玩cancel 玩<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">delay</span></span></strong>!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464220</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你地老母 你地有無搭過飛機架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464168</a><br />\n<br />\n機場現時既建議方法，希望多人睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464007</a><br />\n<br />\n8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：機場人流<br />\n<br />\n[和你飛] 外國人旅遊，中國人滯留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463771</a><br />\n<br />\n離境大堂被阻外國人：應該控制，而唔係阻止登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463192</a>"},{"pid":"10f93f8b78323aece1ce3fa94a8c1b42fd5eae0f","tid":1467953,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e0f8d0bb4d230c07107f2bb97a7b8e7a1a82c97","tid":1467953,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"我地要優先處理中蟈籍航空公司 <img src=\"/assets/fac